aa(lp225
VThe next thing I want to talk about is school feeding.
p226
aVEighty percent of the people in the world
p227
aVhave no food safety net.
p228
aVWhen disaster strikes \u2014
p229
aVthe economy gets blown, people lose a job,
p230
aVfloods, war, conflict,
p231
aVbad governance, all of those things \u2014
p232
aVthere is nothing to fall back on.
p233
aVAnd usually the institutions \u2014
p234
aVchurches, temples, other things \u2014
p235
aVdo not have the resources
p236
aVto provide a safety net.
