aVWhat we have found working with the World Bank
p238
aVis that the poor man's safety net,
p239
aVthe best investment, is school feeding.
p240
aVAnd if you fill the cup
p241
aVwith local agriculture from small farmers,
p242
aVyou have a transformative effect.
